Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:56.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}{\blur5}{\1c&H000000&\3c&H255AF5&}心被压迫被掩盖 {\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HD6A613&}已经不再新鲜
